                                <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch, was
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> in den <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> zu disem mal von
